<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7757563b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1995—Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/104/11">Pub. L. 104–11</ref> designated existing provisions as par. (1), increased number of outlying protection sites from 33 to 39, updated number designation and date on site designation maps, increased total acreage from 8,771 to 14,372 acres, and added par. (2).</p>
